        protected java.sql.Connection getConnection(java.util.Properties props)
                                     throws java.sql.SQLException
        Creates a connection using the specified properties. copied directly from MysqlDataSource.getConnection(). No easy way to override the static `mysqlDriver' without globally affecting the driver.
